metadata.description:
Compelling music knows no bounds. From the Scottish Highlands and the shores of Lake Erie comes a new techno collaboration from producers, Acutek and Dyztopian.

“Elektra Reflections” started as a friendship in the LNRZ Telegram group. J. Thorn producing as Dyztopian shared stems with Acutek, who crafted the raw material into mesmerising beats, hypnotic loops, and an entrancing soundscape.

And in the true spirit of collaboration, Acutek sent the track to Conor Dalton who mastered the track.

Cover art generated by J. Thorn’s prompts in Midjourney, including the golden egg variation.

Don’t sleep on this one-of-kind unique song from two musicians who believe in the power of music, collaboration, and community.

Acutek – https://linktr.ee/Acutek
Dyztopian – https://dyztopian.com/
Conor Dalton – https://linktr.ee/conordalton
